Mintspace routes:
    * Homeroute ->
            -  http://mintspace/           ***(PROTECTED ROUTE PARTIALLY PROTECTED)
                    - / GET REQ
                    - /{id}/ GET REQ  
    * LoginRoute ->
            -  http://mintspace/login/
                    - / GET REQ
                    - / POST REQ
    * SignupRoute ->
            -   http://mintspace/signup/
                    - / GET REQ
                    - / POST REQ
    * ProfileRoute ->               
            -   http://mintspace/profile/   ***(PROTECTED ROUTE)
                    - / GET REQ
                    - / POST REQ
    * BlogCreateRoute ->                    ***(PROTECTED ROUTE)
            -   http://mintspace/write/
                    - / GET REQ
                    - / POST REQ
    * AdminRoute ->                         ***(PROTECTED ROUTE REQUIRES ADMIN PREVILEDGE)
            -   http://mintspace/admin
                    - / GET REQ
                    - / POST REQ




* Home route without auth verification should display blogs with regular tags,
    and with auth verification both regular and premimum vlogs can be shown.



* Blog object structure ->
        - ID
        - AuthorEmail
        - IsPremium
        - Title
        - Content

* User object structure ->
        - Email
        - Name
        - IsAdmin
        - DateOfBirth
        - ProfileCreatedDate
        - EncryptedPassword

* LoginRequest structure ->
        - Email
        - Password

* SignupRequest structure ->
        - Email
        - Name
        - Password
        - DateOfBirth